nd explanations to explore Exoscale&amp;rsquo;s offering. It is organized into the following sections, each building upon the previous one. You can access a section directly by clicking on the corresponding card, but if you want to get the most out of this workshop it&amp;rsquo;s recommended you follow the section in order, starting with the presentation of the &lt;a href="./votingapp"&gt;VotingApp&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>